<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Paramour" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Paramour,</orth> 1) mistress: <bibl n="shak. mnd 4.2.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. IV, 2, 12</bibl>. 13 (not understood by Quince). <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.1.23" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 1, 23</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.3.82" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 82</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 5.3.105" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. V, 3, 105</bibl>.<lb />2) lover: <cit><quote>hag of all despite, encompassed with thy lustful --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.2.53" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 2, 53</bibl></cit>.
